high_descs: walk through kitchen to face counter top under the microwave
pick up the butter knife from the counter top
move to the left to face the shelf right of the microwave with a loaf of bread and purple soap pumper
open the cabinet door above the shelf, put the knife into the glass inside the cabinet
pick up the glass, close the cabinet door
continue to face the same way, move gaze down to the shelf
put the glass on the shelf to the right of the purple soap pumper
anns.task_desc: put a glass and knife onto a kitchen shelf

high_descs: Turn left and walk across the room, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the butter knife off of the counter.
Turn right and walk over to the counter, then turn left and look up.
Open the left cabinet door and put the butter knife in the glass that is in the cabinet.
Take the glass with the butter knife in it out of the cabinet and close the cabinet door.
Look down at the counter, then look up at the upper part of the counter.
Put the glass with the butter knife in it on the upper part of the counter in front of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put a glass with a butter knife in it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn left and walk forward across the room and turn left just before reaching the sink, then walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn right and walk forward to the counter, then turn left towards the cabinets above the bread.
Open the left cabinet and put the knife inside the cup.
Pick up the cup from the cabinet and close the cabinet door.
Bend down towards the shelf below the cabinets containing the bread.
Put the cup on the shelf, in front of the egg.
anns.task_desc: Put a cup with a knife in it on a shelf.
